{
  "slug": "accessibility-feedback",
  "title": "Accessibility Feedback | Pet Emergency Center Florida",
  "description": "We are committed to making our website accessible to all visitors. Report accessibility issues or share feedback so we can improve. Pet Emergency Center.",
  "ogTitle": "Accessibility Feedback | Pet Emergency Center",
  "ogDescription": "Help us make our website usable for everyone. Share accessibility feedback or report issues you encounter.",
  "extraStyles": ["styles/services.css"],
  "main": "<main id=\"main\">\n\n  <section id=\"top\" class=\"pec-svc-hero\">\n    <div class=\"pec-svc-hero__inner\">\n      <div class=\"pec-svc-hero__grid\">\n        <div>\n          <div class=\"pec-hero__eyebrow\"><span class=\"pec-dot\"></span> Help Us Improve</div>\n          <h1 class=\"pec-h1\">Accessibility <span class=\"pec-h1__accent\">Feedback</span>.</h1>\n          <p class=\"pec-svc-hero__sub\">We want our website to be usable for everyone. If you encounter an accessibility issue or have feedback that would help us improve, please let us know.</p>\n          <div class=\"pec-svc-hero__cta\">\n            <a href=\"#feedback-form\" class=\"pec-btn pec-btn--primary pec-btn--lg\"><svg width=\"20\" height=\"20\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#i-shield\"/></svg> Submit Feedback</a>\n            <a href=\"tel:9547720420\" class=\"pec-btn pec-btn--outline pec-btn--lg\"><svg width=\"20\" height=\"20\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#i-phone\"/></svg> Call (954) 772-0420</a>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"pec-svc-hero__media\">\n          <div class=\"pec-svc-hero__art\"><span class=\"pec-svc-hero__chip\">For Everyone</span><img src=\"../img/home-empathy.jpg\" alt=\"Pet Emergency Center reception area\"></div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"pec-narr pec-narr--center\">\n    <div class=\"pec-wrap\">\n      <div class=\"pec-eyebrow\">Our commitment</div>\n      <h2 class=\"pec-h2\">Our Commitment to Accessibility.</h2>\n      <p>Pet Emergency Center believes that every pet owner should be able to use our website to find information, contact us, and access care for their pet. We work to maintain conformance with the Web Content Accessibility Guidelines (WCAG) 2.1 at the AA level, and we continue to improve as standards evolve.</p>\n      <p><strong>Accessibility is an ongoing process, not a one-time project.</strong> We genuinely appreciate visitors who take the time to point out problems we have not noticed.</p>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section id=\"feedback-form\" class=\"pec-narr pec-narr--tint\">\n    <div class=\"pec-wrap\">\n      <div class=\"pec-eyebrow\">Submit feedback</div>\n      <h2 class=\"pec-h2\">Tell Us What You Encountered.</h2>\n      <p>Use the form below to describe an accessibility issue, share a suggestion, or request information in an alternative format. We read every submission.</p>\n      <form class=\"pec-form\" action=\"mailto:accessibility@petemergencycenters.com\" method=\"POST\" enctype=\"text/plain\" style=\"max-width:none\">\n        <div class=\"pec-form__row pec-form__row--two\">\n          <div class=\"pec-form__row\"><label for=\"a-name\">Name <span style=\"text-transform:none;font-weight:500;color:var(--pec-muted);letter-spacing:0\">(optional)</span></label><input id=\"a-name\" name=\"name\" type=\"text\"></div>\n          <div class=\"pec-form__row\"><label for=\"a-email\">Email <span style=\"text-transform:none;font-weight:500;color:var(--pec-muted);letter-spacing:0\">(optional, for follow-up)</span></label><input id=\"a-email\" name=\"email\" type=\"email\"></div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"pec-form__row pec-form__row--two\">\n          <div class=\"pec-form__row\"><label for=\"a-phone\">Phone <span style=\"text-transform:none;font-weight:500;color:var(--pec-muted);letter-spacing:0\">(optional)</span></label><input id=\"a-phone\" name=\"phone\" type=\"tel\"></div>\n          <div class=\"pec-form__row\">\n            <label for=\"a-type\">Type of feedback</label>\n            <select id=\"a-type\" name=\"type\" required>\n              <option value=\"\">Select one</option>\n              <option>Accessibility issue</option>\n              <option>Suggestion</option>\n              <option>Alternative format request</option>\n              <option>Other</option>\n            </select>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"pec-form__row\"><label for=\"a-page\">Page or URL affected <span style=\"text-transform:none;font-weight:500;color:var(--pec-muted);letter-spacing:0\">(optional)</span></label><input id=\"a-page\" name=\"page\" type=\"text\" placeholder=\"e.g. /telemedicine/\"></div>\n        <div class=\"pec-form__row\"><label for=\"a-tech\">Assistive technology used <span style=\"text-transform:none;font-weight:500;color:var(--pec-muted);letter-spacing:0\">(optional, helps us reproduce)</span></label><input id=\"a-tech\" name=\"tech\" type=\"text\" placeholder=\"e.g. NVDA, VoiceOver, keyboard only\"></div>\n        <div class=\"pec-form__row\">\n          <label for=\"a-description\">Description</label>\n          <textarea id=\"a-description\" name=\"description\" required placeholder=\"What did you encounter and what were you trying to do?\"></textarea>\n        </div>\n        <button type=\"submit\" class=\"pec-btn pec-btn--primary pec-btn--lg pec-form__submit\">Send Feedback</button>\n      </form>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"pec-cards\">\n    <div class=\"pec-wrap\">\n      <div class=\"pec-section-head\"><div class=\"pec-eyebrow\">Other ways to reach us</div><h2 class=\"pec-h2\">If the Form Is Not Accessible to You.</h2><p class=\"pec-section-head__sub\">Please reach us through any of the following:</p></div>\n      <div class=\"pec-cards__grid pec-cards__grid--3\">\n        <article class=\"pec-card\"><h3>Phone</h3><p><a href=\"tel:9547720420\" class=\"pec-link\">(954) 772-0420</a> during operating hours.</p></article>\n        <article class=\"pec-card\"><h3>Email</h3><p><a href=\"mailto:accessibility@petemergencycenters.com\" class=\"pec-link\">accessibility@petemergencycenters.com</a></p></article>\n        <article class=\"pec-card\"><h3>In Person</h3><p>Visit us at 921 East Cypress Creek Road, Fort Lauderdale, FL 33334. We are open weeknights and 24/7 on weekends and holidays.</p></article>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"pec-narr pec-narr--center\">\n    <div class=\"pec-wrap\">\n      <h2 class=\"pec-h2\">Thank You for Helping Us Make Our Website Better.</h2>\n      <p>If you ever need information from our website in a different format, just ask. <strong>We are happy to help.</strong></p>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n</main>"
}
